title: October 30th Options Now Available For SouFun Holdings (SFUN)
content:
at 11:42 AM EDT Investors in SouFun Holdings Ltd (SFUN) saw new options begin trading today, for the October 30th expiration. At Stock Options Channel, our YieldBoost formula has looked up and down the SFUN options chain for the new October 30th contracts and identified one put and one call contract of particular interest.
